    </full-screen-media>

    <section class="bg-white py-24 md:py-32 px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-5">
            <div class="md:col-span-2">
                @include('_partials.cloudinary-image', ['url' => 'https://res.cloudinary.com/skystone/image/upload/w_550,c_scale/v1584844609/Jack_Dooley_1_fk6f0u.jpg', 'alt' => 'Portrait photo of Jack Dooley, Skystone CEO'])
            </div>
            <div class="md:px-8 md:col-span-3">
                <p class="text-xl mb-4">At Skystone, we build higher quality buildings faster and more efficiently using modular technology.</p>

                <p class="mb-4">We operate as a Volumetric Modular Manufacturer, with core capabilities in Design and Manufacturing, delivering even the most challenging projects.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">We are uniquely positioned to deliver projects globally with Skystone owned and operated manufacturing facilities in both Europe and Asia.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Our experience in performing full turnkey solutions in North America, on some of the worlds largest modular projects shows we deeply understand all aspects of modular construction right through to transport and installation.</p>
                <p class="mb-4 font-bold">The future is already here, and it is Modular.</p>

